beer_brewer_name: Leinenkugel Brewing Company (Tenth & Blake Beer Co.)
review_blob: No Head and a cheap beer odor disguised this brew. It had a crisp flavor with just a hint of sweetness.
After walking up and down the beer iasle at the local Shop-Rite I often end up buting this because of the incredible savings in exchange for the odd puppy piss flavor. You simply cant beat the price.
